{"type": "article", "id": 17170, "title": "木质圆灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-06T06:29:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122435CNZDmI7btyWh4zlE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这四盏木制灯的灵感源于轮盘桌，虽然它们外形不同，却容易令人产生在旋转的错觉。棕色的木条上有很自然的花纹，间隔以黑色的金属，小巧古雅，且在灯罩上衬出漂亮的光泽。灯上穿引的线做了不同程度的弯曲，增添了生动的气质。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144321LgaZo6Ct0AdH3Mp7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261443228xi2qkmFyMutZgTQ.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144322x1Pmb2eZDpIzGKs5.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144322Jul0Nwh2UQfePOmr.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}